carter john c  university of alabama press log in  account info cart  checkout       join our mailing list    browse authors a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z last name  john c carter john c carter is a civil war enthusiast and independent researcher employed by christopher newport university in newport news virginia books by john c carter   our staff  pharmaceutical process development  formulation optimization  process troubleshooting  carter pharmaceutical consulting our staff   john c carter president career history since joining the pharmaceutical industry in  john carter has held key positions with increasing responsibilities in the field of drug product development he has personally developed many products for novopharm as well as product line extensions for sandoz and marion merrell dow  mr carter has managed teams responsible for the planning and execution of many product development projects through the stages of smallscale development trials scaleup registration and validation examples include generic versions of zantac™ aleve™ altace™ nuprin™ and tagamet™   as director of pharmaceutical development for novopharm mr carter has been responsible for the direct activities of pharmaceutical development staff consisting of formulation development process development  optimization clinical packaging and documentation mr carter also played a key role in providing input for the regulatory submission process involving us canadian and european regulatory agencies  in his role as manager of technical services for novopharm mr carter was responsible for trouble shooting and resolving formulation andor manufacturing problems since starting carter pharmaceutical consulting inc in  mr carter has been involved in the development of new drug products and in the troubleshooting and resolution of manufacturing problems for many pharmaceutical companies clients include branded generic biotech and contract focused businesses in both canada and the united states mr carters experience in the pharmaceutical industry allows him to provide his clients with a technically sound yet timeconscious approach to servicing their technical needs and he is fully aware of the importance of bringing each project to a cost efficient completion education honours food and drug technology diploma – durham college of applied arts and technology oshawa ontario  bachelor of science  –university of waterloo waterloo ontario  achievements  durham college deans list entered directly into rd year of food and drug technology program with advanced standing  durham college silver medal award as the highest ranking graduate of any year technology program  chemistry institute of canada award  ontario scholar   experience nov present  carter pharmaceutical consulting inc previously known as pharmaceutical solutions president  – nov   patheon inc director pds technical services  –     novopharm limited director pharmaceutical development  manager formulation development   –   genpharm inc manager validation  –      novopharm limited manager technical services  –       marion merrell dow canada inc manager product development  –  sandoz canada inc product development chemist  quality control senior analyst      carter pharmaceutical consulting inc  the queensway n rr keswick on lp c phone  fax  home services laboratory tour equipment list our staff news articles links terms sitemap contact us    carter pharmaceutical inc all rights reserved website design office on demandca carter john c  smithville mo  read reviews  get a bid  buildzoom × want a quote from carter john c we recommend getting  quotes for any construction project use our free bidding system to get a quote from carter john c   more of the best tell us about your project is this your business claim now  c bz score  license  re smithville mo carter john c this is my business contact us bz score  write a review summary this is my business request a quote home  search updated may   overview car